{
  "texts": [
    "Concurrently, we developed a multi-agent framework for real-world problem-solving.",
    "This framework distinguishes itself through dynamic task decomposition and automatic subagent creation.",
    "Our benchmark focuses on agent-assisted travel planning.",
    "Concretely, agents in our benchmark are required to act as personal assistants, leveraging computer tools like the databases and the code interpreter to execute tasks.",
    "To provide a holistic evaluation, our benchmark encompasses a spectrum of tasks, each varying in complexity."
  ]
}